text:
We had a great stay at Dunstan and Ananda's very cute bungalow in a quiet neighborhood in Austin.  It's right across the street from a running trail and there are a few amazing restaurants just down the street--Julio's Cafe and the Quack Bakery were both amazing.

The place was very clean and the bed was comfortable.  I'd definitely stay again!
title: Hyde Park Bungalow close to UT & DT
